---
// Replaces the fake customer testimonials + "avg Growth customer saves $14.8K" claims
// with honest industry-benchmark framing. Every stat below is either:
//   - a public industry benchmark (with a plain-language source note), or
//   - a product capability target measured on the engineering bench, not a customer outcome.
// When we have real customer data we'll restore the quote cards.
---
<section id="proof" class="relative bg-navy-900 text-white py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,1) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 80px 80px;"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow text-prizm-400 reveal">The math, honestly</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-h1 font-bold reveal">
        Industry numbers you can look up.<br/>
        <span class="text-white/50">Product targets we can measure.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-white/70 reveal max-w-2xl">
        LogisticsPrizm is pre-launch — we don&#39;t have customer testimonials to publish yet, and we won&#39;t
        make any up. Here is where the industry stands today and what we&#39;ve built to change it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-8">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-prizm-400">&lt;60<span class="text-2xl text-white/60">s</span></div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">AI quote target · product spec</p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          We&#39;ve engineered the quote pipeline to return structured pricing in under a minute.
          Industry benchmark for manual quoting: <strong class="text-white">3–6 hours</strong> per RFQ.
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-5 text-xs text-white/50">Source: Cargofive, 2025 freight-forwarder survey</footer>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-8">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-prizm-400">3–7%</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">of freight spend, typically leaked to invoice errors</p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          The invoice-reconciliation engine is designed to surface that waste per-shipment.
          For a $10M forwarder that&#39;s $300K–$700K a year.
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-5 text-xs text-white/50">Source: Freightify, 2025 revenue-leakage report</footer>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-8">
        <div class="text-5xl font-bold text-prizm-400">15–30</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/60 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider">disconnected systems per mid-market forwarder</p>
        <p class="mt-5 text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
          We built LogisticsPrizm to replace that stack with one data model, one login, and one monthly bill.
          The unification itself is the product.
        </p>
        <footer class="mt-5 text-xs text-white/50">Source: Logi-Sys, fragmented-freight study, 2024</footer>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 reveal">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end justify-between gap-6 rounded-2xl border border-prizm-500/40 bg-gradient-to-br from-prizm-500/10 to-transparent p-8">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <p class="eyebrow text-prizm-400">Quick math, not a sales pitch</p>
          <h3 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold">What would even 3% of your freight spend cover?</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-white/75">
            If you move $5M/year, that&#39;s $150K. Our Growth plan is $4,788/year billed annually.
            We&#39;ll help you model the reconciliation recovery on your actual lanes during the demo —
            no magic numbers, just your invoices.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="/request-demo?calc=1"
          class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-prizm-500 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-prizm-600 transition-colors"
        >Model the ROI with us<span aria-hidden>→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
